@endpoint GET /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Network/ipGroups
@desc Gets all IpGroups in a resource group.
@required {resourceGroupName: any # The name of the resource group.}
@returns(200) Request successful. The operation returns a list of ipGroups resources.

